Global GaN Wafer Defect Inspection System Market Insights
GaN Wafer Defect Inspection System Market size was valued at USD 0.75 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.0% from 2024 to 2030.

GaN Wafer Defect Inspection System Market Overview
The GaN Wafer Defect Inspection System Market is projected to witness robust growth due to the increasing demand for high-performance semiconductors in applications such as power electronics, automotive, and telecommunications. As of 2023, the market value stands at approximately USD 2.7 billion and is expected to reach USD 5.4 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 10.7%. This growth is driven by the rising adoption of GaN wafers in next-generation devices and the ongoing advancements in semiconductor manufacturing processes.

